    dc:description "FIGURES 57 – 64. Xiphidiopsis (Dinoxiphidiopsis) expressa sp. nov. 57, 58. male in habitats. 59. head and pronotum of male in lateral view; 60 – 62. male abdomen terminal in rear dorsal, ventral, lateral view; 63, 64. female abdomen terminal in ventral and lateral view." ;
